<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>SUNPAR LUCHIN CHINH U CH13</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Vawlei mi vialte nih zoh tuah, Ngaihchiatnak a ing Jesuh, A ral vialte
 a tei dih cang, Mi vialte nih khan an biak.

[C1]
   Sun-par luchin sun-par luchin, Bawi Jesuh kha chinhter tuah. A
   lianngan bik Bawi Jesuh kha Siangpahrang, siangpahrang chin.

[V2]
 Vancung khua ummi vialte nih, Bawi Jesuh a thang an that, Biaceih
 thutdan cung an thutter, Vancung mi nih an lawmh tawn.

[C2]
   Sun-par luchin sun-par luchin, Bawi Jesuh kha chinhter tuah. A
   lianngan bik Bawi Jesuh kha Siangpahrang, siangpahrang chin.

[V3]
 Hling luchin kha misual mi nih, Bawi Jesuh kha an chinhter, Mithiang
 mi le vancung mi nih, Jesuh min kha an thangthat.

[C3]
   Sun-par luchin sun-par luchin, Bawi Jesuh kha chinhter tuah. A
   lianngan bik Bawi Jesuh kha Siangpahrang, siangpahrang chin.

[V4]
 Amah hlorh in au cio tuah u! Ral tei lawmhnak kha an tuah. Sunparnak
 ngan bik a hmuh cang. Zohtuah! Bawi Jesuh a si.

[C4]
   Sun-par luchin sun-par luchin, Bawi Jesuh kha chinhter tuah. A
   lianngan bik Bawi Jesuh kha Siangpahrang, siangpahrang chin.</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
<hymn_number>13</hymn_number>
</song>